Chinese Banks’ Bad Loans to Rise in Next Few Years, CLSA Says

-- B y   S o p h i e   L e u n g
-- 
2011-09-19T08:48:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/chinese-banks-bad-loans-to-rise-in-next-few-years-clsa-says.html
Chinese banks’ bad loans may rise
in the next few years, Andy Rothman, China macro strategist at
CLSA Asia Pacific Markets, said at a media briefing in  Hong Kong 
today.  Local government debt isn’t a “looming risk” because it’s
backed by the central government, he said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
